          "solution_type": "detailed",
          "content_html": "Chiral: 1-chloro-2-methylpentane, 3-chloro-2-methylpentane, 2-chloro-4-methylpentane Achiral: 2-chloro-2-methylpentane, 1-chloro-4-methylpentane\n<br><img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc2daIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--f3979a6d7ca71a4458d1b42273f4e2f825f5f14a/OSX_OrgChem_10_DD_A-EC10-3a_img.jpg\" alt=\"A condensed formula for 1-chloro-2-methylpentane.\">\n<br><img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc1FaIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--af12c807dce1ba16a07cc4722f4cdd66fe69abd7/OSX_OrgChem_10_DD_A-EC10-3b_img.jpg\" alt=\"A condensed formula for 2-chloro-2-methylpentane.\">\n<br><img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc1VaIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--55984476e2135c6c6d34481fc118b6581eeb48ba/OSX_OrgChem_10_DD_A-EC10-3c_img.jpg\" alt=\"A condensed formula for 3-chloro-2-methylpentane.\">\n<br><img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc1laIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--db8a5257f7b32dcbd3fbf53f571fbb5cc640ecb9/OSX_OrgChem_10_DD_A-EC10-3d_img.jpg\" alt=\"A condensed formula for 2-chloro-4-methylpentane.\">\n<br><img class=\"scaled-down\" src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBc2NaIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--e20d9b9ecbbdcd6f5ab9b5d19c8bb13f8005caf3/OSX_OrgChem_10_DD_A-EC10-3e_img.jpg\" alt=\"A condensed formula for 1-chloro-4-methylpentane.\">"
